[SN]TITLE[SN]
Christmas: Tears, tantrums and sitting with Santa

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
If you think it is every child's wish to meet Santa, think again.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
When you arrange for the meeting to take place, at a shopping centre or makeshift grotto, you might be beaming with pride and excitement.
However, the little ones you have brought along may not be quite as enthusiastic...
